Windows Modern Icon Pack — Credits and Sources
==============================================

This icon pack is a curated derivative work. Individual icons were selected
from the following upstream Windows-11-style icon packs and then adjusted
where needed.

Upstream packs used during curation
-----------------------------------

- Eleven
- Cobalt
- Windows-Eleven
- Windows-Beuty
- Win11
- We10X
- Fluent
- Fluentwin

